sql:
SELECT agency_name, agency_phone
FROM agencies
ORDER BY agency_name ASC;

external_knowledge:
Malaysia is a popular tourist destination; 

 Travel agencies operate through various channels (e.g., online, offline) to sell trips to Malaysia; 

 The agency type can be a travel agency or a broker; 

 Average net sales is a performance metric for agencies; 

 Claims are typically related to travel insurance; 

 Loyalty programs are used by agencies to retain customers.
